Management of Patients with Type 2 Diabetes with Once-Weekly Semaglutide Versus 
Dulaglutide, Exenatide ER, Liraglutide and Lixisenatide: A Cost-Effectiveness 
Analysis in the Danish Setting.

Gæde P(1), Johansen P(2), Tikkanen CK(3), Pollock RF(4), Hunt B(5), Malkin 
SJP(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Endocrinology and Cardiology, Slagelse Hospital, Slagelse, 
Denmark.
(2)Novo Nordisk A/S, Søborg, Denmark.
(3)Novo Nordisk Scandinavia AB, Copenhagen, Denmark.
